<p>Many of Nancy's fans commented on the post, thanking her for sharing the handy tip. </p>

<p>One wrote: 'As someone with terrible vision who works in healthcare and needs to wear a mask for long hours you are saving my life right now!'</p>

<p>Another commented: 'Thank you for that Nancy. You are an absolute genius.'</p>

